#: ../../docs/tutorials/3d/csg_tools.rst:49
msgid ""
"**Union:** Geometry of both primitives is merged, intersecting geometry is "
"removed."
msgstr ""
"**Union (和集合):** プリミティブのジオメトリを結合させて、共通部分のジオメト"
"リは除去されます。"

